title: Jinjja Hoosier
description: Jinjja, in Korean, means real. Hoosier is just a person from Indiana.

items.title: Welcome to Jinjja Hoosier
items.content_html: Welcome to Jinjja Hoosier, "a blog about nothing". More accurately, a blog not focused on one topic. I'm leaving this blog wide open. We'll see what happens.
